					<div class="absolute top-3 left-3 text-11 font-medium text-white bg-cyan-600/90 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-full px-2.5 py-1 border border-white/20">Новое</div>
				</div>
				<div class="p-4">
					<div class="flex items-start justify-between">
						<div>
							<h3 class="text-base font-semibold tracking-tight text-neutral-100">Полная покраска Audi A6</h3>
							<p class="text-xs text-neutral-400 mt-1 flex items-center gap-1">
								<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="w-3.5 h-3.5 stroke-[1.5]">
									<path d="M7.5 4.21l4.5 2.6 4.5-2.6"></path>
									<path d="M7.5 19.79V14.6L3 12"></path>
									<path d="M21 12l-4.5 2.6v5.19"></path>
									<path d="M3.27 6.96L12 12.01l8.73-5.05"></path>
									<path d="M12 22.08V12"></path>
								</svg>
								Полная покраска в камере
							</p>
						</div>
						<div class="text-right">
							<div class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-100">5 дней</div>
							<div class="text-11 text-neutral-400">Декабрь 2024</div>
